{
  "id": "adv_event_2111_01_04",
  "title": "アイドルだって",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "チケット完売だって、怜ちゃん\n私達二人だけだから心配してたけど、よかったね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tickets are sold out‚ Rei-chan!\nI was worried because it was just the two of us‚ but this is great!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8,
      "endTime": 9.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.466666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "うん。よかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… Great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.466666666666669,
      "endTime": 11.666666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣もいろんな人呼んじゃったから\nもしガラガラだったらどうしよって思ってたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I invited all kinds of people‚\nso I was worried what we’d do if the place was empty.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.866666666666667,
      "endTime": 18.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "うん。よかったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… It’s a relief.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3,
      "endTime": 20.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "……怜ちゃん？　ねえねえ、聞いてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan? Hey‚ are you listening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.76666666666667,
      "endTime": 25.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……え？\n……うん、聞いてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?\nYes‚ I’m listening.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5,
      "endTime": 29,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "きっと怜ちゃんのご両親も来てくれるよ\n……チケットは渡せたんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure your parents will show up.\nYou gave them their tickets‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2,
      "endTime": 36.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.56666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "渡すことは、出来たわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did manage to give them the tickets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.56666666666667,
      "endTime": 38.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 40.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "お父さん、私のライブに来てほしいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Father‚ I really want you to come to my live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.26666666666667,
      "endTime": 44.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 44.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何度も言わせるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t make me say it over and over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8,
      "endTime": 47.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私は、お前の仕事を認めてはいないと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t accept your job—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2,
      "endTime": 50.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 50.333333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "私、決めた。お父さんが来てくれるまで、何度でも誘う\n来てくれるまで、絶対にアイドルを辞めない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My mind’s made up. I’m going to keep on inviting you\nuntil you come‚ and I won’t quit being an idol until you come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.333333333333336,
      "endTime": 59.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-reidad002.m4a",
      "text": "……怜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5333333333333,
      "endTime": 60.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 60.93333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんが反対する理由も、分かる\n間違ってるとも思わない。心配してくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand why you’re against my work.\nI don’t think you’re wrong‚ and I thank you for worrying about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.93333333333333,
      "endTime": 69.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-reidad003.m4a",
      "text": "そう思うなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that’s what you think…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3,
      "endTime": 70.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 71
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "でも……一つだけ言わせて……\nアイドルだって……誰かを救うことが出来るの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… let me just say one thing.\nIdols have the power to save people too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71,
      "endTime": 79.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 79.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "自意識過剰かもしれない。でも、私達のために\nお金や時間を使って会いに来てくれる人がいるんだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe I’m being too self-conscious‚ but there are people\nwho spend their time and money to come and see us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.86666666666666,
      "endTime": 88.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "会えてよかったって。明日から頑張れるって\nそう言ってくれるの。それが私の……希望にもなるの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hearing them say they’re glad to see us‚ and that they can\ngo on trying for another day…that is what I feel hopeful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.86666666666666,
      "endTime": 97.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 98.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……続けたところで、成功する訳がない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You won't succeed with doing that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.16666666666669,
      "endTime": 102.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれない\nでも、成功してもしなくても、私は続ける",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You may be right.\nBut I’m going to keep going‚ whether I succeed or not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 109.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-reidad005.m4a",
      "text": "……いつかはアイドルを辞める日が来るだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…One day‚ you’re going to quit being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.533333333333,
      "endTime": 114.39619067509936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 109.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その先はどうするつもりだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you planning to do after that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.63333333333334,
      "endTime": 114.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "――今は分からない\n毎日、目の前のことを頑張るだけで精一杯だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know right now.\nI have my hands full with doing my best on the next thing every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117,
      "endTime": 123.56666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私はアイドルになって、よかったと思う\n今が人生で一番、充実してる。絶対に後悔しない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’m glad I became an idol.\nNow I’m living my life to the fullest‚ and I’ll never regret that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.76666666666667,
      "endTime": 133.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 133.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_04-reidad006.m4a",
      "text": "そんな甘い考えで、幸せになれるはずがない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That kind of naive thinking will never make you happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 139.41752818425496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうして私の言うことが聞けないんだ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why won’t you listen to what I say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1,
      "endTime": 139.76666666666662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
